==紀念碑==
[[File:Memorial_anglichanam.JPG|thumb]]
[[File:Dmitry_Medvedev_in_Azerbaijan_3_July_2008-8.jpg|thumb]][[德米特里·阿纳托利耶维奇·梅德韦杰夫|梅德韦杰夫]]前往{{le|永恆火焰紀念碑|Eternal Flame (Azerbaijan)}}致意]]
{{le|永恆火焰紀念碑|Eternal Flame (Azerbaijan)}}位於烈士長廊中，[[亞塞拜然總統|亞塞拜然總統]]與政要時常前往該處致意<ref name="mirtv.ru">{{cite web|date=May 11, 2007|url=http://mirtv.ru/content/view/19362/42/|script-title=ru:На Аллее Шехидов в Баку вновь зажегся Вечный огонь05.11.2007 20:35|publisher=mirtv.ru|access-date=March 25, 2010|language=ru|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130417042245/http://mirtv.ru/content/view/19362/42/|archive-date=2013-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

墓園中還有{{le|巴庫土耳其烈士紀念碑|Baku Turkish Martyrs' Memorial}}，紀念1918年[[巴庫戰役|巴庫戰役]]中，1130名被布爾什維克與亞美尼亞軍隊殺死的[[土耳其|土耳其]]士兵<ref name="worldbulletin.net">{{cite web|date = April 26, 2009|url = http://www.worldbulletin.net/news_detail.php?id=40745|title = Azerbaijan closes Turkish mosque in Baku: Report|publisher = Sitemiz AA, CÄ°HAN ve Reuters abonesidir|access-date = March 25, 2010|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090428075550/http://www.worldbulletin.net/news_detail.php?id=40745|archive-date = 2009-04-28|dead-url = no}}</ref>。紀念碑旁不遠處有一面牌匾，紀念在同場戰爭中戰死的英國軍人<ref name="timesonline.co.uk">{{cite web|date = January 14, 2003|url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/article812089.ece|title = History denies Baku heroes a memorial|work = [[The_Times|The Times]]|access-date = March 25, 2010|archive-date = 2019-12-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191218012335/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/article812089.ece|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="payvand.com">{{cite web|date = September 20, 2003|url = http://payvand.com/news/03/sep/1124.html|title = Azerbaijan: Planned British War Memorial Raises Hackles|work = NetNative|publisher = Payvand's Iran News|access-date = March 25, 2010|last = Peuch|first = Jean-Christophe|archive-date = 2008-12-10|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081210203843/http://www.payvand.com/news/03/sep/1124.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==安葬名人==
烈士長廊入口處的第一個陵墓為[[黑色一月大屠殺|黑色一月大屠殺]]中遇害的法里薩·阿拉维迪耶夫（Fariza Allahverdiyev）與伊利哈姆·阿拉维迪耶夫（Ilham Allahverdiyev）夫婦，伊利哈姆被蘇軍射殺，法里薩在聽聞丈夫死訊後自殺<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.day.az/print/news/society/190631.html |title=Январский террор проармянской советской власти и непоколебимость героизма азербайджанского народа |date=2010-02-15 |language=ru |accessdate=2020-12-29 |archive-date=2010-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100215134451/http://www.day.az/print/news/society/190631.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azerbembassy.org.cn/rus/jan20_vict0001.html|title=Аллахвердиев Ильгам Аждар оглы, 1962 года рождения|language=ru|accessdate=2020-12-29|archive-date=2012-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227122843/http://www.azerbembassy.org.cn/rus/jan20_vict0001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這座陵墓後來成了愛與忠誠的象徵<ref>{{cite web|url=https://archive.is/20120713091310/http://mirtv.ru/content/view/89323/62/ |title=В Азербайджане вспоминают жертв трагедии 20 января 1990 года|language=ru}}</ref>。在[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]中喪生的記者{{le|欽吉斯·穆斯塔法耶夫
|Chingiz Mustafayev}}與{{le|莎拉廷·阿斯加羅娃|Salatyn Asgarova}}也被安葬在烈士長廊<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ansgroup.ws/az/ans-haqq%C4%B1nda/tesisciler/naxishqiz_mustafayeva.html|title=Təsisçilər Şurası|date=2011-09-04|language=az|accessdate=2020-12-29|archive-date=2011-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904032524/http://www.ansgroup.ws/az/ans-haqq%C4%B1nda/tesisciler/naxishqiz_mustafayeva.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

